records.addlTxt:
The State moves to delete the repeater enhancers on counts 2 and 3.  Motion granted.
NO CONTEST Plea entered to the amended charge in count 2, possession of methamphetamine. Convicted.
NO CONTEST Plea entered to the amended charge in count 3, felony bail jumping. Convicted.
The State moves to dismiss and read in counts 1 and 4.  Motion granted.
On count 2, sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1)	Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
2)	Any other counseling, treatment, assessments as recommended  by the agent;
3)	Pay court costs of $518.00 plus the court costs of $355.00 from count 3;
4)	pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
5)	provide DNA sample;
6)	maintain fulltime employment, schooling, work search or combination; at the agent's discretion;
7)	maintain absolute sobriety;
8)	Submit to random urine screens and pay for same.
On count 3, the court sentences the defendant to the Manitowoc County Jail for thirty (30) days, time served.
Defendant has credit for 30 days.
$355.00 court costs imposed, to be paid as a condition of probation on count 2.
DNA sample ordered.         
Court paperwork is to be mailed to the defendant at Cephas House, 325 Centinel Drive, Waukesha, WI 53189.
Minutes.
